I have been away from this email group for a week and don&#39;t know the 
entire thread. I don&#39;t know what the main discussion was/is. I am 
&#39;handicapped&#39; myself. I have very poor vision and am considered legally 
blind. Working with ITC is very challenging for me but I love it so I do 
it. I use various softwares that help me &#39;see&#39; my pictures. Hand tremors 
can be difficult. 4 years ago they discovered an aneurysm in my brain 
and operated. They had to remove a large portion of my skull because the 
aneurysm was so large. I thank them for saving my life but the resulting 
consequences are hard to deal with. I can&#39;t smell anymore. My left hand 
has no feeling and will do what it wants when I am typing. I have 
tremors in both hands and do type two fingers. In all I guess you could 
say that I am a mess. The only thing is, I don&#39;t consider myself a mess. 
I am having fun. I don&#39;t walk to well anymore and my thinking is always 
screwed up. What my head says and what comes out in talk or typing is 
two entirely different things :-) My writings at time are almost child 
like because the appropriate words won&#39;t come even though I know them. 
In other words, who cares? I don&#39;t. If you don&#39;t like what I am saying 
then that is your problem, not mine. If I post something and you change 
it, &#39;eh, I have the original. I am considering making my own sweep radio 
like Frank&#39;s inventions. It won&#39;t be nearly as good as Franks but hey, I 
can try can&#39;t I? :-)

I have been interested in white noise for years now and now know people 
who also are into it and don&#39;t think I am an idiot.

Al, without knowing what went down, calm down buddy. We are all cool and 
in this together!

:-)

Mick

